description:
Buckle up, I'll guide you through dining out in Italy. 
üçùGet the PDF, Dining in Italy Explainer Guide: https://bit.ly/42utcmI

We'll cover the timing of meals, how to make reservations, and navigating the menu structure. You'll learn about Italian customs, including separate menus for food and wine, and ordering house wine by the liter! U'll also suggest some traditional Italian dishes to try and encourage ordering a combination of plates to create your own Italian feast. And, I'll explain how Italians eat and share some common phrases to help you communicate with the staff.
